This app bundles the FFmpeg command-line binaries at release time as a separate
subprocess (not linked). Those binaries are GPL-licensed and are not committed
here; see src-tauri/binaries/LICENSE and SOURCE.md, and scripts/fetch-ffmpeg.md
for how to obtain them. Invoking FFmpeg as a separate executable (mere
aggregation) does not place this MIT-licensed source under the GPL.
